name: create-a-simple-online-store-that-sells-ai-agents
description:
create a simple online store that sells AI agents

**AI Learning Insights Applied:**
• Invest in customer education and awareness about the benefits and uses of AI agents
• Ensure the AI agents are user-friendly and meet the needs of the target market
• Establish a strong customer service and support system to handle complaints and returns

**Warning Signals to Monitor:**
⚠️ Low customer engagement and interaction with the AI agents
⚠️ High rate of customer complaints or returns
⚠️ Lack of repeat business or customer loyalty
